---
title: Seared Salmon in Sticky Spiced Cranberry Sauce with Truffled Roast Potatoes and Tenderstem® Broccoli
description: Serve up a festive feast this winter! Make a meal that's truly special with this lightly indulgent and luxurious Seared Salmon in Sticky Spiced Cranberry Sauce.
